t=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PYoG8nI.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PYoG8nI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7w5uB4k.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7w5uB4k.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7w5uB4k.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LiWLF0v.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LiWLF0v.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LiWLF0v.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/rRmFba0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rRmFba0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rRmFba0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHy8z0l.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHy8z0l.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHy8z0l.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n民国时期，我们曾经那么文明，优雅，有贵族范，有气质，连外国人都称赞我们中国人文明，有教养;而现在，我们每一个人大部分已经成为了一匹战狼，尤其是留学生，遇到反送中的港人就说出很多很多令人恶心的脏话骂话，甚至动不动就用开豪车、打人等方式侮辱香港人。<br>\n诶，中国人，今非昔比！","date":"2019-08-22","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}